fields.name: Stock Market Price Updater
fields.description: This is a single-page application that retrieves daily stock prices and also allows two years of historical data to be viewed for each stock.
fields.technologies: Flask, React, Webpack, Babel, PostgreSQL, Docker

fields.name: NASA Imagery Fetcher
fields.description: This is an Android app that fetches images from NASA's Image of the Day and Astronomy Picture of the Day services.
